<bibRefCitation id="EFAA2FACFFDDA44BFB99B3AD043DF8F5" author="Boessenecker RW" box="[1149,1393,1777,1799]" pageId="24" pageNumber="1277" pagination="815 - 940" refId="ref23138" refString="Boessenecker RW. 2013. A new marine vertebrate assemblage from the Late Neogene Purisima Formation in Central California, part II: pinnipeds and cetaceans. Geodiversitas 35: 815 - 940." type="journal article" year="2013">Boessenecker, 2013</bibRefCitation>
